{"tid":2246817,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"韓美聯合聲明12年來首次刪除“維持駐韓美軍”的語句","createTime":"2020-10-17T11:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T13:41:56.000Z","uid":75656,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6eb0bab655b17804498a3b222c9db6e5b7424a31","tid":2246817,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T11:12:09.000Z","msg":"當地時間14日，韓美兩國在美國國防部舉行的第52屆韓美安保協議會（SCM）上就防衛費分擔金等問題發生了衝突。在今年的聯合聲明中，應美方要求時隔12年刪除了自2008年起一直寫明的&ldquo;再次確認將駐韓美軍維持在當前水平的承諾&rdquo;的語句。原定舉行的韓美防長的新聞發布會也因故取消。最近，兩國在Quad等待解議案上立場差距不斷拉大，美國的不滿情緒浮出水面。<br />\n<br />\n據朝鮮日報報道，韓美聯合聲明12年來首次刪除&ldquo;維持駐韓美軍&rdquo;的語句。據該報，14日舉行的第52屆韓美安保協議會（SCM）無論是形式，還是內容都引發了爭議。會上還可以感知到美國施壓要求上調防衛費分擔金，以及暗示將裁減駐韓美軍的立場。加之，韓美防長的新聞發布會因美國的&ldquo;內部原因&rdquo;而被突然取消。對此，有分析認為，由於兩國在各項待解議案上的立場差異愈發明顯，引爆了美國的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n當天最大的待解議案是防衛費分擔金問題。美防長在總括髮言中便表示：&ldquo;防衛費負擔不能不公地落到美國納稅人頭上，且為了保障美軍在韓半島的穩定駐紮，有必要儘快達成協議。&rdquo;而徐旭在總括髮言中並未提及防衛費問題。<br />\n<br />\n美防長埃斯珀當天提及&ldquo;美軍的穩定駐紮&rdquo;似乎有意暗示在今後的韓美關係中，駐韓美軍可能成為變量，而非常量。美國還表明立場稱，將把以韓半島防禦為目的的&ldquo;補充戰鬥力（bridging capability）&rdquo;與韓國軍隊的武器獲取計畫聯繫起來。聯合聲明中稱：&ldquo;需要理解韓國的獲取計畫。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n據分析，美國在SCM上表露不滿反映了最近在各個領域都出現摩擦的韓美關係的氛圍。但華盛頓的外交消息人士表示：&ldquo;反華活動已經形成了超黨派氛圍，無論特朗普能否連任，施壓力度都會不斷提高。&rdquo;全權負責反華經濟同盟經濟繁榮網絡（EPN）實際工作的美國國務院副國務卿凱斯&middot;克拉奇當天接受媒體採訪時表示：&ldquo;中共總是盯着軟柿子，但如果世界團結起來，就無法報復&rdquo;，&ldquo;令參與中國&lsquo;一帶一路&rsquo;的（發展中）國家陷入荒廢的大流行即將到來。&rdquo;他還表示：&ldquo;韓國為了本國的安保必須加入清潔網絡。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n據該報道，韓國總統府青瓦台國家安全室長徐薰訪美會見了白宮國家安全顧問，還計畫同美國國務卿蓬佩奧舉行會晤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2/20201017-%E9%9F%93%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E12%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4-%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E9%A7%90%E9%9F%93%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D-%E7%9A%84%E8%AA%9E%E5%8F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25BA%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%2F20201017-%25E9%259F%2593%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E12%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BE%2586%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E5%2588%25AA%25E9%2599%25A4-%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%258C%2581%25E9%25A7%2590%25E9%259F%2593%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BB%258D-%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25AA%259E%25E5%258F%25A5&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao5vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=1cd4d79d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2/20201017-%E9%9F%93%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E12%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4-%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E9%A7%90%E9%9F%93%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D-%E7%9A%84%E8%AA%9E%E5%8F%A5</a>"},{"pid":"8ef4efa4aac9088a7a3b80dfcc03da69e1afcfc7","tid":2246817,"uid":238920,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T11:15:53.000Z","msg":"駐台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e7c8cf7211e20f811b957585f6754cf8d5b5a9","tid":2246817,"uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T11:41:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b684b23fdae99ccc582bcc578ccfea3e7371e53d","tid":2246817,"uid":1524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T11:44:33.000Z","msg":"比金仔食埋南韓<br />\n睇你班左膠仲係咪奶共"},{"pid":"3c2a4ef380bb0d5b3166366ac3bc9b18dd1557f0","tid":2246817,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T11:48:29.000Z","msg":"恩恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028fb293f32785136fa2275e447c1d4c96e8ecc9","tid":2246817,"uid":266342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:45:58.000Z","msg":"駐朝美軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2124ce5735977af3bbdcf5569f9877c56875af","tid":2246817,"uid":109923,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:49:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">髮言</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n支那source<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a579be1f0eeffba087cb85795abdb1f0fc0929","tid":2246817,"uid":282637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:49:23.000Z","msg":"究竟條友後生點解會做維權律師?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876b315268957daf7ab862c7686c134597079d5f","tid":2246817,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:50:49.000Z","msg":"唔好意思可唔可以幫我推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n強烈要求連登仔女全力支持特朗普競選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2246891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2246891</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4df84e4b1aa94f82fffa49f51342881b9173e40d","tid":2246817,"uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1c2124ce5735977af3bbdcf5569f9877c56875af","tid":2246817,"uid":109923,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:49:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">髮言</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n支那source<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:56:53.000Z","msg":"關於法國國際廣播電台<br />\n<br />\n法國國際廣播電台（RFI）用法語和其他十二個語種向全世界廣播。法廣巴黎編輯部與其遍布五大洲的四百名特約記者向聽友推出新聞與專題節目為了解世界提供鑰匙。法廣每周在全球聚集近四千萬聽友，法廣網站、手機應用程序等在內的新媒體每個月的瀏覽數字以上千萬計。<br />\n(* 法語, 英語, 柬埔寨語, 華語, 華語, 西班牙語, 豪薩語, 曼丁哥語, 富拉尼語, 斯瓦西里, 波斯語, 葡萄牙語, 葡萄牙語, 羅馬尼亞語, 俄語, 越南語 )<br />\n<br />\n新聞資料<br />\n<br />\n收聽 收看 世界<br />\n<br />\n法國世界媒體集團（France M&eacute;dias Monde）旗下彙集三語滾動新聞頻道的法蘭西24小時（FRANCE 24），向全世界播放節目的法廣（RFI）和阿拉伯語蒙特卡洛中東台（Monte Carlo Doualiya）。法蘭西24，法廣和蒙特卡洛中東台三個頻道用十四種語言從巴黎向五大洲播放節目<br />\n<br />\n法國世界媒體集團（France M&eacute;dias Monde）記者及其特有的特約記者網通過新聞、採訪報道、專題與辯論等節目為聽眾和觀眾提供放眼世界的新聞時事與多元化的文化與觀點。<br />\n<br />\n每一周，法蘭西24的直接觀眾高達四千一百七十萬；法廣聽眾擁有三千四百五十萬；蒙特卡洛中東台聽眾有六百七十萬。瀏覽 France M&eacute;dias Monde 集團三個台的新媒體每個月總數為兩千四百萬。<br />\n<br />\n法國媒體世界 France M&eacute;dias Monde 集團是法國電視五台 TV5MONDE 的股東與合作夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E6%98%AF%E8%AA%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25AA%25B0&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao5vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=bf85e417\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E6%98%AF%E8%AA%B0</a>"},{"pid":"b6e3ff6e8a3d2f78543837a211aeab387c7fd094","tid":2246817,"uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:58:22.000Z","msg":"未能談妥駐韓美軍費用分攤 美軍方將讓南韓工人休無薪假<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2246939/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2246939/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"be1230875874b829200b6375596faccbc139f196","tid":2246817,"uid":276865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b684b23fdae99ccc582bcc578ccfea3e7371e53d","tid":2246817,"uid":1524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T11:44:33.000Z","msg":"比金仔食埋南韓<br />\n睇你班左膠仲係咪奶共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:00:38.000Z","msg":"食左唔奶咪食子彈囉"},{"pid":"a3936c631a56a342b4ac76bcd5f996d3c85d0e15","tid":2246817,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:37:43.000Z","msg":"過台灣啦<br />\n<br />\n金仔由得奶共寅自己食"},{"pid":"4259c4e0a5582ef355f852e899163e713caa85a0","tid":2246817,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:41:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pmenWgfh954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpmenWgfh954&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao5vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=5fd01259\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pmenWgfh954</a><br />\n就算無駐韓美軍都唔怕啦<br />\n韓仔咁打得，使驚北韓班營養不良矮仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"b6e3ff6e8a3d2f78543837a211aeab387c7fd094","tid":2246817,"uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T12:58:22.000Z","msg":"未能談妥駐韓美軍費用分攤 美軍方將讓南韓工人休無薪假<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2246939/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thre